results.output:
Soft, silken strands swayed, serene, sublime;
Sharp shears severed, stealing summer's springtime.
Such sudden sorrow shadowed sunlit space;
Shorn style showed sorrow's stark, stern face.
Still, spirit stood, surviving savage shear,
Solemn self saw sacrifice so sheer.

